Here’s a self-contained HTML file that recreates the “My Academic Credentials” block closely (responsive, rounded container, warm overlay, serif heading, centered four-column grid, and award-style icons). Save it as `academic-credentials.html` and open in a browser.

```html
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>My Academic Credentials — SG Maths Tuition (replica block)</title>

<!-- Typography close to the original look -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root{
    /* Tweak these if you want even closer color matching */
    --bg-warm: #6e4a33;       /* warm coffee brown */
    --bg-warm-dark: #3a2418;  /* darker brown for overlay mix */
    --text: #fff;
    --text-soft: #f3ebe6;
    --maxw: 1200px;
    --radius: 28px;
    --shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
  }

  /* Page scaffold just to demo the block centered on a neutral background */
  body{
    margin:0;
    background:#0f0f10;
    color:var(--text);
    font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", "Apple Color Emoji","Segoe UI Emoji","Segoe UI Symbol","Noto Color Emoji", sans-serif;
    line-height:1.45;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;
  }
  .wrap{
    padding: min(5vw, 48px);
  }

  /* ===== Credentials Section ===== */
  .credentials{
    position:relative;
    max-width: var(--maxw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    /* Faux bokeh-y background (no external image needed) */
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 500px at 80% -10%, rgba(255,190,120,.18), transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(900px 420px at -10% 0%, rgba(255,205,160,.12), transparent 65%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in oklab, var(--bg-warm) 92%, black 8%), var(--bg-warm-dark));
    isolation:isolate;
  }
  /* Warm glass overlay for depth */
  .credentials::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(35,18,10,.22), rgba(35,18,10,.48));
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index:0;
  }

  .cred-inner{
    position:relative; z-index:1;
    padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);
  }

  .cred-title{
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:.4px;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5.6vw, 64px);
    line-height:1.05;
    text-align:center;
    color: var(--text);
    text-wrap: balance;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;
  }
  .cred-sub{
    text-align:center;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.6vw, 20px);
    max-width: 58ch;
    margin: 0 auto clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 42px);
    text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.18);
  }

  .cred-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 28px);
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px){
    .cred-grid{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px){
    .cred-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .cred-item{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 22px);
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.025));
    outline: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
  }

  .icon{
    width: clamp(64px, 8vw, 92px);
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: clamp(10px, 1.6vw, 14px);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .icon svg{
    width:100%; height:auto; display:block;
  }
  /* Award glyph styling */
  .award-stroke{ stroke: #fff; opacity:.95; }
  .award-fill{ fill: #fff; opacity:.96; }

  .cred-text{
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.1vw, 28px);
    line-height:1.2;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    letter-spacing:.2px;
  }
  .cred-text .line{ display:block; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="credentials" aria-labelledby="cred-title">
      <div class="cred-inner">
        <h2 id="cred-title" class="cred-title">My Academic Credentials</h2>
        <p class="cred-sub">
          My qualifications are your assurance of my expertise. I believe a tutor must have absolute
          mastery of a subject to teach it effectively.
        </p>

        <div class="cred-grid">

          <!-- ITEM 1 -->
          <article class="cred-item">
            <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- minimal laurel-star “award” glyph (inline SVG, no external icon libs) -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img">
                <defs>
                  <filter id="softGlow" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
                    <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="1.2" result="blur"/>
                    <feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
                  </filter>
                </defs>

                <!-- dotted ring -->
                <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="44" fill="none" stroke-width="6"
                        stroke-linecap="round" class="award-stroke"
                        stroke-dasharray="0.1 13" filter="url(#softGlow)"/>
                <!-- star -->
                <polygon class="award-fill"
                         points="60,29 67.6,50.5 90,51.4 71.9,64.6 78.1,86.2 60,73.6 41.9,86.2 48.1,64.6 30,51.4 52.4,50.5"
                         />
                <!-- simplified laurel arcs -->
                <path d="M22,67
                         C25,59 31,52 39,48
                         C34,53 31,59 30,65
                         C27,72 27,72 22,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M98,67
                         C95,59 89,52 81,48
                         C86,53 89,59 90,65
                         C93,72 93,72 98,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="cred-text">
              <span class="line">Ph.D. in</span>
              <span class="line">Mathematics,</span>
              <span class="line">National</span>
              <span class="line">University of</span>
              <span class="line">Singapore (NUS)</span>
            </h3>
          </article>

          <!-- ITEM 2 -->
          <article class="cred-item">
            <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- reuse same glyph -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img">
                <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="44" fill="none" stroke-width="6"
                        stroke-linecap="round" class="award-stroke"
                        stroke-dasharray="0.1 13"/>
                <polygon class="award-fill"
                         points="60,29 67.6,50.5 90,51.4 71.9,64.6 78.1,86.2 60,73.6 41.9,86.2 48.1,64.6 30,51.4 52.4,50.5"/>
                <path d="M22,67 C25,59 31,52 39,48 C34,53 31,59 30,65 C27,72 27,72 22,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M98,67 C95,59 89,52 81,48 C86,53 89,59 90,65 C93,72 93,72 98,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="cred-text">
              <span class="line">B.Sc. First Class</span>
              <span class="line">Honours in</span>
              <span class="line">Mathematics,</span>
              <span class="line">NUS</span>
            </h3>
          </article>

          <!-- ITEM 3 -->
          <article class="cred-item">
            <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img">
                <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="44" fill="none" stroke-width="6"
                        stroke-linecap="round" class="award-stroke"
                        stroke-dasharray="0.1 13"/>
                <polygon class="award-fill"
                         points="60,29 67.6,50.5 90,51.4 71.9,64.6 78.1,86.2 60,73.6 41.9,86.2 48.1,64.6 30,51.4 52.4,50.5"/>
                <path d="M22,67 C25,59 31,52 39,48 C34,53 31,59 30,65 C27,72 27,72 22,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M98,67 C95,59 89,52 81,48 C86,53 89,59 90,65 C93,72 93,72 98,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="cred-text">
              <span class="line">GPA: 4.9 / 5.0</span>
              <span class="line">(Placed on Dean's</span>
              <span class="line">List for 4</span>
              <span class="line">Semesters)</span>
            </h3>
          </article>

          <!-- ITEM 4 -->
          <article class="cred-item">
            <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img">
                <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="44" fill="none" stroke-width="6"
                        stroke-linecap="round" class="award-stroke"
                        stroke-dasharray="0.1 13"/>
                <polygon class="award-fill"
                         points="60,29 67.6,50.5 90,51.4 71.9,64.6 78.1,86.2 60,73.6 41.9,86.2 48.1,64.6 30,51.4 52.4,50.5"/>
                <path d="M22,67 C25,59 31,52 39,48 C34,53 31,59 30,65 C27,72 27,72 22,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M98,67 C95,59 89,52 81,48 C86,53 89,59 90,65 C93,72 93,72 98,78"
                      fill="none" stroke-width="6" class="award-stroke" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="cred-text">
              <span class="line">Associate Faculty,</span>
              <span class="line">Singapore</span>
              <span class="line">University of</span>
              <span class="line">Social Sciences</span>
              <span class="line">(SUSS)</span>
            </h3>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
```

Notes:
- The copy, structure and ordering mirror the live section (“My Academic Credentials”) from your site: heading, short assurance sentence, and the four credentials items with similar line breaks and emphasis. citeturn0view0
- I kept everything in one file (no JS, icons inline as SVG, fonts via Google Fonts). You can swap fonts/colors later to match your global theme exactly.

