Here’s a single-file version with three clear breakpoints (desktop 4-up, tablet 2×2, mobile stacked), **no external fonts**, and on **mobile the card text collapses into one sentence with normal word-wrap** (no forced line breaks). Font sizes only taper slightly as screens shrink.

```html
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>My Academic Credentials — Responsive, No External Fonts</title>

<style>
